        <h1>How to take a screenshot!</h1>
        <p>There are three options for taking a screenshot.</p>
        <h2>Here are the three options:</h2>
    <ul> 
        <li>Command-Shift-3 for the entire page</li>
        <li>Command-Shift-4 to select what you want to screenshot</li>
        <li>Command-Shift-5 to open the screenshot menu</li>
    </ul>
